data.description:
Market time at no fault to seller! Listed and then did some finishings of basement and a few other items so "availability to show" has been sporadic but it is fully open now! Amazing home and price for all it has to offer! Willing to do Interest rate buy down as well :)

Beautiful two story in highly sought after and rarely available Carriage Hill, a tree lined subdivision in the Northland. Situated on a stellar, large corner lot! 2 year old roof, HVAC, AC and Water Heater 2014. Upgraded from 100 to 200 amp electrical service. All new Blown Insulation in attic space accessible from hallway. Newer with hardwoods, custom cabinets in kitchen and baths. Quartz counter tops and island, Stainless appliances stay in kitchen. Sellers added a covered front and back patio to enjoy in the privacy fenced backyard! Installed remote control gas fireplace. Home security system throughout and camera system stays. Brand new carpet in all bedrooms and finished basement. Possible 5th non conforming bedroom in basement! Don't miss out on this incredible home in a fantastic neighborhood and school district!
